\layout Subsubsection

0.22a against 0.21a
\layout Standard

Release 0.22a is mainly a bugfix release against 0.21a.
\layout Itemize

All know (crash-inducing) bugs fixed.
 
\layout Itemize

Message editor/viewer improvements, adding clipboard support and selections.
 
\layout Itemize

wxGTK layout bug fixes - German, French, Spanish translations 
\layout Itemize

